description: I met a real tough guy today. Tattoos, wrist bends, baseball cap, you get the picture. Really smart with money, too. Two loans and a mortgage, 32 000 in total. He kept promising to pay me back as soon as possible if I help him out. But I didn´t believe him, guys like him can´t be taken seriously. Anyone who owns a gold "Fuck you" statue of a middle finger cannot be taken seriously. Not to mention that I wanted something else from him. After initial struggle he agreed to become my toy. He even tried very hard to make me cum. I guess, he wanted it to be over soon. They sometimes try to do this. That´s why I carry my red friend in my bag. I was also in the mood for improvisation, thank god I found that stupid gold statue. I hope the boy learned the lesson.
title: Debt Dandy 147
